1. UUsee is a commercial P2P streaming system
2. Paper using an algorithm called Ration to provision
bandwidth to the streaming server.  Ration will find the 
minimum  server capacity within an ISP to divi-up the
 capacity amung the channels.
3. Ration itself uses time series forecasting and dynamic 
regression techniques taking into account number of peers,
stream quality, streaming server bandwith usage.  A limited
window of history is used to determine the prediction.
4. Uses heuristic inc. water filling approach to solve problem.